1. on linux
    vi ~/.subversion/auth/svn.simple/<file name>
    
    K 8
    passtype
    V 6
    simple
    K 8
    password
    V *
    <password>
    K 15
    svn:realmstring
    V *
    <svn url> *
    K 8
    username
    V *
    <user name>
    END
    
2. on OS X
    (1) shift+command+u （实用工具）
    (2) Open keychain access（钥匙串访问）
    (3) Under "Keychains" on the left, choose "login" （“钥匙串”->“登录”）
    (4) Under "Category" below, choose "All items" （“种类”->“所有项目”）
    (5) At the top right in the search box, type in the the host URL (e.g. svn) （右上角查找）
    (6) Your keychain item will show if you chose to have your Mac remember your login credentials.
    (7) Double click the item and check the "Show password" checkbox at the bottom of the dialog that pops up. 
        You will have to enter your Mac login to reveal the password. （双击->“显示密码”）
